[{'description': 'fraction, time to transfer the reefer between different modes of transport', 'id': '68f592ea-ec5e-40c3-8c86-c952c0763fc4', 'unit': 'dimensionless', 'comment': 'Estimated value.

The time the reefer is in operation is calculated using different average speed of all the different modes of transport (train, lorry, ship, etc.). This parameter presents an additional time during which the reefer is in operation, but is not being transported; the time when the reefer is being transfered from one type of transport to another.
